{"word":"ἐπιχωρέω","slug":"ἐπιχωρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιχωρέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to give way, yield</i>, <el>τινί</el> to one, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to forgive</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to come towards, join as an ally</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>accedere alicui</el>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>to go against</i> the enemy, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}